<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Box Model · Práctica</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, 'Segoe UI', monospace;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f0f2f5, #dce1e8);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .playground {
      max-width: 900px;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      border-radius: 32px;
      padding: 2rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #0f172a;
      letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    }
    .demo-card {
      background-color: #ffe6b3;
      width: 320px;
      border: 8px solid #2b9348; 
      padding: 32px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      border-radius: 24px;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    
   
    .demo-card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;        
      color: #1e293b;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-align: justify;    
      margin-bottom: 16px;     
    }
    
     .demo-card p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .label-box {
      background: #2b9348; 
      color: white;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 60px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    
    .inspector {
      background: #f1f5f9;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      margin-top: 28px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: monospace;
      border: 1px dashed #64748b;
    }
    .highlight {
      background: #facc15;
      padding: 2px 5px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .flex-buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    button {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #2b9348;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 40px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.1s;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    button:hover {
      background: #2b9348;
      color: white;
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }
    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      .demo-card { width: 260px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px auto; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="playground">
  <h2>📐 El Modelo de Caja (Box Model)</h2>
  
  <div class="demo-card" id="cajaDemo">
    <span class="label-box">CONTENIDO</span>
    
    <p>
      <strong>✨ Content ✨</strong><br> 
      Este es el área de contenido de nuestro elemento. Su ancho (<span class="highlight">width</span>) y su alto (<span class="highlight">height</span>) delimitan el espacio interior disponible.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      🔹 <strong>Padding</strong> → Espacio interno colocado alrededor del texto.<br>
      🔹 <strong>Border</strong> → Línea o borde sólido de color verde.<br>
      🔹 <strong>Margin</strong> → Separación o espacio externo con otras cajas.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="inspector">
    💡 <strong>Información del Box Model:</strong><br>
    🟩 content + 🟦 padding + 🟢 border + ⬜ margin = espacio total.<br>
    ¡Modifica los valores en el editor de la izquierda!
  </div>
  
  <div class="flex-buttons">
    <button onclick="alert('Edita los estilos en el panel izquierdo → Cambia padding, margin, border, width')">🧪 Experimentar</button>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
